high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the back of the kitchen to the black round table
Pick up the yellow handled knife from the table
Turn to the left and walk to the kitchen counter in between the sink and stove and face it
Slice the apple on the table
Open the cabinet door below
Place the knife inside the cabinet and close the door
Face back towards the kitchen counter
Pick up the apple slice from the counter
Turn around and walk towards the left to the microwave
Open the microwave place the apple inside, warm it then remove it
Turn around and walk straight towards the refrigerator on the right and face it
Open the refrigerator and place the apple inside then close the door
anns.task_desc: Cooking a sliced apple in the microwave

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the black table then turn right and walk to the white fridge, then hang left and walk to the table on your left
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle that is sitting on the table
Head to across the room to your left to the counter that is to the left of the sink
Slice the apple that is on the counter
Take a step backward
Open the cabinet that is under the counter containing the apply and to the left of the stove.  Place the knife in the cabinet and then close the door
Step forward toward the counter containing the apple
Pick up a slice of the apple
Turn around then head to the microwave that is to your left
Open the microwave and place the apple inside in front of the mug then close the microwave and turn it on. Then open the microwave and pick up the apple then close the door
Turn around and head to the black table across the room then turn right and walk to the white fridge
Open the fridge and place the apple on the top shelf in between the two mugs then close the fridge
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple into a fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the table then turn right and walk to the fridge then turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the table.
Pick up the yellow handled knife.
Turn left and take a step left then walk to the counter then turn right and take a step then turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the stove top to face an apple.
Cut the apple into three chunks,.
Back up a step.
Put the knife in the cabinet under the apple the one directly to the right of the stove.
Walk to the counter and take a step left.
Pick up a chunk of apple.
Turn right and take a step to your right then walk to the microwave that's in front of you.
Warm the chunk of apple in the microwave and then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the table then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold chunk of apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Move to stand at the round black table, so you're positioned directly right of the chair.
Pick up the sharp knife with the yellow handle.
Carry the knife to the counter space between the stove and sink.
Use the knife to slice the green apple on the counter.
Back up from the counter while carrying the knife so you have room to open the cupboard.
Open the cupboard beneath the apple and place the knife inside.
Move back closer to the counter where the apple is.
Pick up a slice of apple from the counter.
Carry the apple slice to the microwave.
Place the apple slice in the microwave and then remove, once heated.
Carry the heated apple slice to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the apple slice on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk across the room to the dining table, once there walk to the right hand side of the chair.
Pick up the knife on the table, in front of the pump bottle and loaf of bread.
Turn to your left and walk to the kitchen counter, on your left, between the stove and the sink.
Cut the apple, on the counter, in front of the tea kettle into slices.
Step back from the counter.
Place the knife in the bottom, left cupboard, under the counter the apple is on.
Step back up to the counter the apple is sitting on.
Pick up one of the apple slices from the kitchen counter.
Turn to your right and walk to the microwave on the kitchen counter across from you.
Place the apple in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the apple from the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen to the table, turn right at the table and go to the refrigerator.
Place the apple in the refrigerator, on the right shelf, above the drawers.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm apple slice in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the round table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn around and go to the counter by the sink.
Slice the apple on the counter.
Go to the cabinet under the counter.
Put the knife in the cabinet.
Go to the counter.
Pick up an apple slice on the counter.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator
Put the apple slice in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved apple slice in the refrigerator.
